The SABC board is briefing MPs on its decision to reappoint Hlaudi Motsoeneng to a top executive position. The SABC board is briefing the Communications Portfolio Committee on its decision to reappoint Hlaudi Motsoeneng to a high level executive position. A court has found that he was illegally appointed to the position of chief operating officer. The SABC board though reappointed him to the position of group executive for corporate affairs. The African National Congress' National Executive Committee (NEC) and Cabinet have said its decision to reappoint Motsoeneng was wrong. Watch the briefing live.  